blog.name: fearlessrep89
blog.title: FearlessRep89
blog.description:
Amanda. Columbus, OH. Born in 1989, too.

Lover of dogs, my wife and Taylor Alison Swift.

07-17-18 in Cleveland = all my pieces fell into place.

body:
03/01/19 5:54am

I’m just timestamping the potentially last post I’ll ever write in the rep era™️, which is a crazy ass thing to type, number one. Number two, the rep era brought out the best in me. And I will forever love these past 18ish months. Everything fell into place during this era. I quit smoking, I got married, I met Taylor… it was magical, wild, perfect and life changing. Thank you Taylor. I love you. @taylorswift
